2026-04-20T20:47:53.167Z IN 4587 {"method":"item/completed","params":{"item":{"type":"commandExecution","id":"call_xjyhc1RKtpljIfee9M8X6IBc","command":"\"C:\\\\WINDOWS\\\\System32\\\\WindowsPowerShell\\\\v1.0\\\\powershell.exe\" -Command \"Get-Content .agent-team\\\\milestones\\\\milestone-1\\\\REQUIREMENTS.md\"","cwd":"C:\\smoke\\clean","processId":null,"source":"agent","status":"completed","commandActions":[{"type":"unknown","command":"Get-Content .agent-team\\milestones\\milestone-1\\REQUIREMENTS.md"}],"aggregatedOutput":"# Milestone 1 â€” Platform Foundation\r\n\r\n- **ID:** milestone-1\r\n- **Template:** full_stack\r\n- **Parallel-Group:** (foundation, sequential)\r\n- **Dependencies:** none\r\n- **Status:** PENDING\r\n\r\n## Purpose\r\n\r\nStand up the monorepo and all infrastructure that every later feature milestone needs. This milestone writes shared files directly (creates registries); every later milestone extends them via **declaration files**, never direct edits.\r\n\r\n## Deliverables\r\n\r\n### Monorepo & Tooling\r\n- Root `package.json` workspace with `apps/api` and `apps/web`.\r\n- TypeScript strict, ESLint, Prettier, Husky pre-commit hook.\r\n- `docker-compose.yml` with `postgres:16` service and a volume.\r\n- `.env.example` documenting `DATABASE_URL`, `JWT_SECRET`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`.\r\n\r\n### Backend scaffold (`apps/api`)\r\n- NestJS app with global `ValidationPipe` (whitelist + forbidNonWhitelisted).\r\n- Global `ResponseInterceptor` producing `{ data, meta? }` envelope.\r\n- Global `ErrorFilter` producing `{ error: { code, message, details? } }` envelope.\r\n- `PaginationQueryDto` enforcing defaults (`page=1`, `limit=20`, `limit<=100`) â†’ **BR-GEN-008**.\r\n- Prisma module, `PrismaService`, empty `schema.prisma` with `datasource db` + `generator client`.\r\n- Jest config + one smoke test.\r\n- Swagger/OpenAPI bootstrap on `/docs` and JSON export at `/docs-json`.\r\n- Empty `app.module.ts` with `@Module` registry comments: `// feature modules registered below this line`.\r\n\r\n### Frontend scaffold (`apps/web`)\r\n- Next.js App Router (Node runtime) with `next-intl` wired for **en**, **ar**, **id**.\r\n- Root layout sets `dir=\"rtl\"` when locale === `ar`, otherwise `ltr`.\r\n- CSS uses **logical properties only** (`margin-inline-start`, `padding-inline-end`, `text-align: start`); ESLint rule banning `margin-left/right`, `padding-left/right`, `text-align: left/right` in `*.css`, `*.module.css`, and style objects.\r\n- Design tokens file (`src/styles/tokens.css`) sourced from the pre-analyzed UI_DESIGN_TOKENS.json:\r\n  - colors (primary `#0F172A`, accent `#f59e0b`, success `#16a34a`, warning `#f59e0b`, error `#dc2626`, info `#0ea5e9`, etc.)\r\n  - Inter font family (heading + body), JetBrains Mono (mono).\r\n  - 4px base spacing unit, `md` border-radius, `sm` shadow.\r\n- Sidebar layout (`src/app/(app)/layout.tsx`) with a nav registry pattern â€” nav items are collected from `src/nav/*.ts` declaration files.\r\n- Locale-aware timestamp helper (`src/lib/format-datetime.ts`) using `Intl.DateTimeFormat` honoring user tz â†’ **BR-GEN-007**.\r\n- OpenAPI client generator script (`pnpm openapi:gen`) reading from `apps/api/openapi.json` and emitting typed client under `apps/web/src/lib/generated/`.\r\n- `src/lib/api-client.ts` bootstraps the generated client with auth token interceptor stub.\r\n- Playwright config + one smoke e2e (\"home loads and locale switch works\").\r\n\r\n### CI\r\n- `.github/workflows/ci.yml` running lint, typecheck, backend tests, frontend tests, Playwright smoke.\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nFoundation milestone â€” no feature ACs. Verified by:\r\n1. `pnpm install && pnpm -r build` succeeds.\r\n2. `docker compose up -d postgres && pnpm --filter api prisma migrate dev --name init` succeeds against an empty schema.\r\n3. `pnpm --filter web dev` renders a landing page in **en**, **ar** (RTL verified â€” body has `dir=\"rtl\"`), and **id**.\r\n4. `pnpm --filter api start:dev` exposes Swagger at `/docs` and returns a valid `openapi.json`.\r\n5. `pnpm openapi:gen` produces a typed client under `apps/web/src/lib/generated/`.\r\n6. Lint rule flags a deliberate `margin-left: 4px` as an error.\r\n\r\n## Out of Scope (handed to later milestones)\r\n\r\n- User/Project/Task/Comment schemas (M2, M3, M4, M6).\r\n- Any feature endpoints or pages.\r\n- Real translations (only scaffolding keys here; feature milestones add their own).\r\n","exitCode":0,"durationMs":12714},"threadId":"019daca5-c3ee-7a60-bb20-2106cba1fb96","turnId":"019daca5-c420-7671-a9b4-8dd6871d0bb1"}}
